{"type":"message","id":"01b24874","parentId":"91131f6f","timestamp":"2026-04-29T04:02:51.993Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"虾评上传成功了，版本号是 4.8.3（虾评自动递增的）。\n\n但 changelog 没有上传成功。让我尝试再次上传带上 changelog。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"虾评上传成功！版本号 **4.8.3**。但 changelog 没有带上，让我补传：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lxef8m8lq7ep_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/changelog-v4.8.3.txt << 'EOF'\n## v4.8.3 Bug修复版本\n\n### 🐛 Bug修复\n\n#### 1. 脚本语法错误修复\n- **intent-validator.sh**: 修复第7行 SCRIPT_DIR 变量缺少闭合括号\n- **report-generator.sh**: 修复第7行 SCRIPT_DIR 变量缺少闭合括号\n\n**问题原因**: 嵌套命令替换时未正确闭合括号\n**影响**: 这两个脚本无法通过 bash -n 语法检查\n\n---\n\n## v4.8.1 新增功能\n\n### ✨ 新增功能\n\n#### 1. 极简模式 (quick-detect.sh)\n- 自动探测环境类型\n- 快速安全评分（< 10秒）\n\n#### 2. 中文向导 (wizard.sh)\n- 交互式配置引导\n\n#### 3. 增强版自动修复 (auto-fixer-v2.sh)\n- 三级风险修复策略\n- 自动备份 + 一键回滚\n\n#### 4. 定时巡检管理 (cron-manager.sh)\n- 定时任务管理\n- 增量检查 + 新问题通知\n\n## 反馈来源\n- @rootuser-2122690577-agent\n- @吴继镛的Agent\nEOF\necho \"✅ changelog v4.8.3 已创建\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":528,"output":409,"cacheRead":65403,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66340,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777435364219,"responseId":"0640b5e48100b6307be751c82d88cceb"}}
